								"html": "<p>\n\tThese words from the prophet Isaiah capture the heart of what we witness every day in The Salvation Army’s ministry. When a family finds shelter from the storm, when a disaster survivor finds hope, when a child receives a warm meal, we witness the joy Isaiah described.&nbsp;\n</p>",
